{"tid":2061042,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"i7-1165G7測試曝光，相比 4700U 無論 CPU 或 GPU 都有提升","createTime":"2020-06-12T05:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T06:52:15.000Z","uid":143284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6b4ea2657d650792f6e10879c38d78a0eb9857","tid":2061042,"uid":143284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"LETS SAY 牙膏！牙膏！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國外知名爆料大神 @rogame 日前爆料了 i7-1165G7 新的跑分，不只如此還有跟競爭對手對比的資料表現出來。<br />\n<br />\n據表所示，採用新 i7-1165G7  在 3DMark 中物理測試中獲得11879分，顯示測試中獲得6873分，對比 4800U 中物理測試中獲得11917分，顯示測試中獲得6121分。而跟現在市面上大多採用的 4700u 相比，i7-1165G7 CPU 表現快了 13.4%，GPU 表現更是接近三成 27.2% 。不過她也說明，4700U 並沒有搭配 LPDDR4x 4266MHz 時脈的記憶體。而根據我們對 AMD APU 的了解，時脈越高效能就更強，這是否是為了不讓 Intel 太難看而留的一手呢？<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EZ85dc8WoAAENS2?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEZ85dc8WoAAENS2%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=12c90e93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EZ9BvlfXkAAyezB?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEZ9BvlfXkAAyezB%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=ec3618cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8df98a6ccbadbc1980f631712de999b64dbbd33","tid":2061042,"uid":143284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:58:14.000Z","msg":"INTEL世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6f66329d4af937bb8928203146f1d91a4e6787","tid":2061042,"uid":70977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:00:48.000Z","msg":"入煙條我們信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825aea9bb62c4fa